children.name:
Expect $(`[data-testid="login.signin.message"]`) to have text containing
                
                Expected: "Please try again"
                Received: "Your account has been blocked. Please contact Telnyx support for information regarding your account."
Test login with valid credentials for blocked account

Expect $(`[aria-label="signup-form_error"]`) to have text containing
                
                Expected: "recaptcha"
                Received: "reCAPTCHA validation required"
Test sign Up with valid credentials with captcha

Expect $(`[aria-label="signup-form_error"]`) to have text containing
                
                Expected: "recaptcha"
                Received: undefined
Test sign Up with valid credentials with captcha

Expect $(`[id="email_error"]`) to have text containing
                
                Expected: "Please enter a valid email address"
                Received: "This field is required."
Test sign Up with incorrect email
Test login with an invalid email
